  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业PLC系统的流程图，核心是三个组件：现场的执行器控制器、PLC逻辑单元，还有MQTT Broker。整个流程从用户认证开始，到最后把GPO配置下发到执行器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三个节点横向排列还是纵向？另外GPOs是指组策略对象吗？在工业物联网场景里具体指什么配置？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GPOs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "纵向从上到下吧，逻辑更清晰。GPOs在这里是通用输出配置（General Purpose Outputs），就是PLC要下发给执行器的控制参数。流程是：执行器先找PLC认证用户，PLC再去Broker拉取配置，拿到后解析并应用到执行器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把三个节点竖着排好，从上到下依次是ActuatorController、PLC Logic、MQTT Broker，然后画第一条线——从执行器到PLC，标注\"authenticate user\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "authenticate user"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但方向注意一下，是执行器指向PLC，表示它发起认证请求。接下来PLC要去Broker拉配置，这条线是从PLC往上指到Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "fetch GPOs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上PLC到Broker的线，标注\"fetch GPOs\"。然后Broker需要把配置回传吧？我画一条返回线，标\"relevant GPOs resolved\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "relevant GPOs resolved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，最后一步最关键：PLC解析这些GPOs然后应用到执行器。这条线是从PLC指回执行器，标注\"parse GPOs and apply\"，形成一个完整的闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，四条连线都画好了。我检查一下：执行器→PLC（认证），PLC→Broker（拉取），Broker→PLC（返回配置），PLC→执行器（解析应用）。结构是完整的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个流程准确反映了我们工业PLC的工作机制。MQTT Broker作为配置中心，PLC做逻辑中枢，执行器最终落地控制，整个数据流清晰明了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
